\"removed\")).isFalse();\n        assertThat(restored.get(\"missing\", 42)).isEqualTo(42);\n        assertThat(restored.getKeys()).containsExactlyInAnyOrder(\"first\", \"second\", \"third\");\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] serialize(ObjToIntMap value) throws Exception {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n\n        try (ObjectOutputStream objectOutputStream = new ObjectOutputStream(outputStream)) {\n            objectOutputStream.writeObject(value);\n        }\n\n        return outputStream.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static ObjToIntMap deserialize(byte[] serialized) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream objectInputStream = new ObjectInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(serialized))) {\n            return (ObjToIntMap) objectInputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 14538, "output": 1015, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 15553, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777674285209, "responseId": "resp_09fed1433f49acbc0169f5282d88f881a39a118f43c0abc772"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_dKRk3QS1Wv1DpS8Pbl6f6aIe|fc_09fed1433f49acbc0169f528352d4481a3a3eb98337432df35", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2006 bytes to tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/java/org_mozilla/rhino/ObjToIntMapTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777674294736}]}
